    <briefdescription>
<para>It provides additional methods for handling component state so it can be saved, restored and cleared. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>An optional interface to be implemented by components in addition to the <computeroutput><ref refid="class_open_oasis_1_1_i_linkable_component" kindref="compound">ILinkableComponent</ref></computeroutput> interface. It can be left completely to the component to handle persistence of state or it can also implement <computeroutput><ref refid="class_open_oasis_1_1_i_byte_state_converter" kindref="compound">IByteStateConverter</ref></computeroutput> and provide ways for state to be converted to and from an array of bytes. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
